description.en-us: Eastwood Automobilia is a brand of larger scale model vehicles owned by Liberty Classics based out of Dyersville, Iowa. Hot Wheels has released many products under the label since 1996 including a "Limited Edition" coin bank series and collaboration Lionel train car. Each 1997 coin bank included a single removable key attached to the underside that was used to retrieve coins. Later 1998 releases omitted this feature.
